
- Installation:

-- install Groovy:

  http://groovy.codehaus.org

-- make sure the compiled Groovy emitter is newer than the source code:

  touch Emitter.pmc


- Usage:

-- compiling from MiniPerl6 to Groovy:

  perl mp6-jvm.pl < hello.pl > hello.groovy
  ~/groovy-1.0/bin/groovy hello.groovy


- Development:

-- recompiling Emitter.pm

  perl mp6.pl < Emitter.pm > Emitter.pmc

